I had only a short time to test Chromantic Halo (as I said I was not 50 at that time and I don’t grouped again with the person so far) but the mob beat me almost dead with out triggering the Chromantic Halo wards. Therefore I think the spell is of limited use.<br />
What experiences do you have with the wards? Maybe they are different then mine. Do you use Chromatic Barrier often? I tried it only few times but I start to miss Fire Barrier very fast and I switch back. Have you already learned Chromantic Halo?
                  
