                  I have really difficulties to disagree with you on the rune thing. I don’t have the experience to predict what the future holds but if I would be a developer and if I developed a cool mob ability I would not like that a stupid rune is killing my cool ability. It would be really too bad if that would be the same for the counter system as well. It would scrap a functionality I really liked (even it needs some major improvement).<br />
